#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:54
msgid "What is a Price Blueprint?"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:55
msgid ""
"A Price Blueprint is a set of rules that controls how the price of a product "
"is built. Instead of setting a fixed price on each product, you define the "
"rules once in a template and then attach that template to as many products "
"as you like."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:56
msgid ""
"When you update a rule in the template, every product that uses it will "
"immediately reflect the new price — no need to edit products one by one."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:57
msgid ""
"Each product still has its own base price. The template only controls the "
"add-ons that get added on top of that base."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:61
msgid "What is a Rule?"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:62
msgid ""
"Each rule answers the question: \"If the customer picks this option, how "
"much extra should be added to the price?\""
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:63
msgid "A rule has three parts:"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:65 templates/admin-repeater.php:36
msgid "Attribute"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:65
msgid ""
"The characteristic being chosen, for example Color or Size. These come from "
"your WooCommerce global attributes."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:66 templates/admin-repeater.php:37
msgid "Value"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:66
msgid "The specific option the customer picks, for example Red or Large."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:67
msgid "Price add-on"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:67
msgid ""
"The amount added to the base price when this option is selected. Set it to 0 "
"if the option should cost nothing extra."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:69
msgid ""
"You can add as many rules as you need. Use the filter box to quickly find a "
"rule when the list gets long."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:70
msgid ""
"To temporarily disable a rule without deleting it, use the toggle next to "
"it. Disabled rules are saved but ignored when calculating prices."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:74
msgid "How the Final Price is Calculated"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:75
msgid "The price the customer pays is always:"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:76
msgid "Base price + add-ons for each selected option = Total"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:77
msgid ""
"Example: a product has a base price of $20. The customer picks Color → Red (+"
"$5) and Size → Large (+$3). The total is $20 + $5 + $3 = $28."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:78
msgid ""
"On the shop and product page, the displayed price shows the lowest possible "
"total (\"From $X\"), calculated using the cheapest option for each attribute."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:79
msgid ""
"The price shown to the customer updates instantly as they make selections — "
"no page reload needed."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:80
msgid ""
"If you update a rule after a customer has already added the product to their "
"cart, the new price will apply the next time they visit the cart."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:84
msgid "Attaching a Template to a Product"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:86
msgid "Save your Price Blueprint first."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:87
msgid ""
"Go to Products and open the product you want to configure (or create a new "
"one)."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:88
msgid ""
"In the Product Data section, change the product type to Configurable Product."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:89
msgid ""
"Open the General tab and set a base price — this is the starting price "
"before any options are added."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:90
msgid "Open the PriceBlueprint tab and select the template from the dropdown."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:91
msgid "Save the product."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:93
msgid ""
"The same template can be assigned to multiple products. Each product keeps "
"its own base price."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:97
msgid "Quick tips"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:99
msgid "Set a price add-on of 0 to offer a free option."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:100
msgid "One template can be shared across many products."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:101
msgid "Updating a rule takes effect immediately — no need to re-save products."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/HelpTab.php:102
msgid "Disable a rule to hide it from customers without losing it."
msgstr ""

